OL,3,CParents' concerns over thousands of
OL,4,Csuspensions at two schools
OL,6,FA mayor has arranged a public meeting
OL,7,Fto allow parents to express their
OL,8,Fconcerns about thousands of
OL,9,Fsuspensions at two schools in Cornwall.
OL,11,FMayor of Camborne James Ball has
OL,12,Fcalled the meeting after being
OL,13,Fcontacted by around 50 parents raising
OL,14,Fconcerns about Camborne Science and
OL,15,FInternational Academy (CSIA) and Pool
OL,16,FAcademy.
OL,18,FAlmost 3000 suspensions were handed
OL,19,Fout at CSIA in the 2023-24 academic
OL,20,Fyear, according to figures from the
OL,21,FDepartment for Education.
