OL,3,CParents' concerns over thousands of
OL,4,Csuspensions at two schools
OL,6,FCllr Ball, who also represents
OL,7,FCamborne Roskear & Tuckingmill on
OL,8,FCornwall Council as an independent,
OL,9,Fsaid the issue was "massive" and he's
OL,10,Fholding a meeting on 25 February.
OL,12,FA spokesperson for the Athena Learning
OL,13,FTrust, which runs both CSIA and Pool
OL,14,FAcademy, said the schools "care deeply
OL,15,Fabout the wellbeing and happiness of
OL,16,Fevery young person".
