OL,3,CParents' concerns over thousands of
OL,4,Csuspensions at two schools
OL,6,FCllr Ball said parents have been
OL,7,Fraising concerns over behaviour,
OL,8,Fsuspensions and special educational
OL,9,Fneeds and disabilities (SEND)
OL,10,Fprovision at the two schools.
OL,12,FAccording to Department for Education
OL,13,Ffigures, CSIA suspended 2,967 pupils
OL,14,Fduring the 2023-24 academic year - the
OL,15,Fsecond highest number of any school in
OL,16,FEngland.
