OL,3,CParents' concerns over thousands of
OL,4,Csuspensions at two schools
OL,6,FCllr Ball said the meeting will enable
OL,7,Fhim to listen to parents' concerns,
OL,8,Fbefore a meeting with senior leaders
OL,9,Fat CSIA and Pool Academy, as well as
OL,10,Fthe chair of Athena Learning Trust,
OL,11,Fwhich he hopes will take place in
OL,12,FMarch.
OL,14,F"When I started this, I didn't think
OL,15,Fit would be this big ` it's massive,"
OL,16,Fhe said.
