OL,3,CParents' concerns over thousands of
OL,4,Csuspensions at two schools
OL,6,F"I have been contacted by about 50
OL,7,Fparents. It's a case of now working
OL,8,Fwith the schools and the parents
OL,9,Fconstructively to get everyone's
OL,10,Fvoices heard.
OL,12,FHe said the meeting will not provide
OL,13,F"full answers to any issues" as he
OL,14,Fneeds to "gather information."
OL,16,F"This will not be an attack meeting,"
OL,17,Fhe said. "We need to work
OL,18,Fconstructively."
