OL,3,CParents' concerns over thousands of
OL,4,Csuspensions at two schools
OL,6,FCllr Ball added: "There's some
OL,7,Fconfusion about what the schools will
OL,8,Fdo and what the parents expect the
OL,9,Fschools to do.
OL,11,F"It's a complicated issue with many
OL,12,Fparents feeling their children are
OL,13,Ffalling through the net for various
OL,14,Freasons.
OL,16,F"I think there are quite a few parents
OL,17,Fwho feel their voices aren't being
OL,18,Fheard and their children are being let
OL,19,Fdown. The most important thing in all
OL,20,Fthis is that we're there for the young
OL,21,Fpeople."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
