OL,3,CParents' concerns over thousands of
OL,4,Csuspensions at two schools
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Athena Learning
OL,7,FTrust said: "Our schools care deeply
OL,8,Fabout the wellbeing and happiness of
OL,9,Fevery young person and we recognise
OL,10,Fhow important it is for parents and
OL,11,Fcarers to feel heard and supported.
OL,13,F"If families have any concerns about
OL,14,Ftheir child and their experiences at
OL,15,Fschool, we always encourage them to
OL,16,Fcome to us directly. That way, we can
OL,17,Fwork together quickly and sensitively
OL,18,Fto help them.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
