OL,3,CParents' concerns over thousands of
OL,4,Csuspensions at two schools
OL,6,F"We value our partnerships with
OL,7,Fparents, carers and other local
OL,8,Fstakeholders and we are committed to
OL,9,Fdoing everything we can to help our
OL,10,Fstudents thrive.
OL,12,F"We're here to listen and families can
OL,13,Falways speak to their school if they
OL,14,Fneed support or advice."
OL,16,FThe public meeting will take place at
OL,17,F7pm on 25 February at Holmans Social
OL,18,FClub in Camborne.
OL,20,FCredit: Lee Trewhela, LDRS
